# FocusFlow вЂ” Production-Ready Implementation Plan

## Goal
Transform FocusFlow from a client-side prototype into a production-ready full-stack application with a Node.js backend, real Google OAuth, PostgreSQL persistence, Redis caching, and hardened integrations.

