## Frontend Changes (Minimal)

Only these files change on the frontend:

| File | Change |
|---|---|
| **`LoginScreen.tsx`** | Replace fake form в†’ single "Sign in with Google" button that navigates to `GET /auth/google` |
| **`PermissionScreen.tsx`** | Remove Google token input (auto-connected). Keep Slack + Jira manual token inputs. Wire "Save" to `POST /api/integrations/:provider` |
| **`Dashboard.tsx`** | Replace direct API calls в†’ call `GET /api/inbox` and `POST /api/analyze` via the backend |
| **`services/api.ts`** | NEW: Centralized fetch wrapper that includes credentials (`fetch(url, { credentials: 'include' })`) |
| **`services/geminiService.ts`** | DELETE вЂ” moved to server |
| **`services/integrationService.ts`** | DELETE вЂ” moved to server |
| **`vite.config.ts`** | Add proxy: `/api` в†’ `http://localhost:3001`, `/auth` в†’ `http://localhost:3001` |
| **`App.tsx`** | Add auth state check on mount (`GET /auth/me`). If unauthenticated в†’ show login. If authed в†’ go to dashboard |

