## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `docker-compose up -d` в†’ verify Postgres + Redis are healthy
- Run `npm run dev` (both frontend + backend via concurrently)
- Test Google OAuth login flow end-to-end in the browser
- Test inbox fetch with real Google credentials
- Test Slack/Jira integration save + proxy fetch
- Test AI analysis with caching (first call hits Gemini, second returns cached)
- Verify session persistence across page refreshes
- Verify logout destroys session

### Manual Verification
- Check browser DevTools в†’ confirm no API keys or tokens in network requests
- Check cookies в†’ confirm `httpOnly`, `Secure`, `SameSite` flags
- Check PostgreSQL в†’ confirm tokens are encrypted (not plaintext)
- Test on mobile viewport в†’ confirm responsive layout
